Faldatouch is a framework to add multi-pointer/multi-user support to pygame applications.

It was developer during pyCamp 2011[0] by members of Python Argentina[1].

Faldatouch is free software, distribued under the GPL V3 license

[0] http://python.org.ar/pyar/PyCamp/2011/
[1] http://python.org.ar/

